Shouldn't have a ridge that soon but you'll need to bust the glaze and
install new rings.
I'd look at the rod bearing from the overheated cylinder to be sure it
isn't hammered out.
I've got a single Mahle cylinder and piston if you need it, $40.00,
$48.00 with rings installed.

